      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ILIKEITLIKETHAT (1) was responsible for a very good effort last time over 1684m at this track, finishing third and just 1.3 metres from the winner. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Good enough to take out a race like this. NEVELE ARMA (4) is at the track for the first time. By Huntsville and hails from the Dylan Egerton-Green stable. Trial winner who looks above average. Will be ready to run a big race. SWEET ROBBIE (6) faces the starter for the first time. By Sweet Lou and hails from the Aiden De Campo stable. Was not far away in a recent trial. Any push in betting will add to the confidence. ROCK THE TOUR (8) is a two-year-old colt from the Aiden De Campo stable on debut. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Was not far away in a recent trial. Has the right credentials to play a major role.",
